<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākēbdē rasaratnabhānugaṇitē māsē tapassaṁjñikē śuklā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>vāsarē budhadinē śrīsiṁhaśailēśituḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādāt puṣpamayasrajaṁ pratidi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>naṁ svābhīṣṭasaṁsiddhayē śrīmān sāhasamallatōnnatapada<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīkṛṣṇadāsapra
<lb n="4" break="no"/>bhuḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1296 gunēṁṭi māgha śukla pratipadayu bu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dhavāramunāṁḍu muda<unclear>ri</unclear>kiṭisāha<supplied reason="omitted">sa</supplied>mallaṁḍu tana bhāryya Annamanāyu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟālikiṁ buṇyābhivṛddigā śrīnarasi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>hanāthuniki nityamunnu Oka ti
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rumāla cātanu varadunāyaka varadunāyuni koḍuku ciṁgaricēta
<lb n="8"/>nālu māḍalaku kuṁcaprasādamu ṭhāvuvaṭi bisuvāḷi bhīmani
<lb n="9" break="no"/>kiṁ beṭṭenu tammināyaka purāyināyunicētanu reṁḍu māḍalaku O
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ka puṣpavāṭika gaṭṭu viricipeṭṭenu Ī bhīmaṁḍu pūvulu decci nitya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>munnu tirumāla veṭṭi Ī kuṁcaṁḍu prasādamunnu bhujiṁpaṁgalāṁ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḍu Ī dharmuvu Ācaṁdrārkkasthahigāṁ beṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pāla
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi(<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) śatrusyādharmmaḥ śatrurna kasyacit
<lb n="14"/>Ī dharmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 0 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>śrī</unclear> śrī śrī śrī
</p>

